Package units

Class Assasin

java.lang.Object
units.Droid
units.Assasin
public class Assasin extends Droid
The Assasin class represents a specialized type of Droid with unique attributes and abilities. This droid has the ability to attack its enemy multiple times in a row using its special ability.
